Package: RCognito
Type: Package
Title: A Simplified Interface for Amazon Cognito
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sanjaya J Shetty
Maintainer: Sanjaya J Shetty <shettysanjaya01@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides a user-friendly API wrapper around Amazon Cognito services, simplifying user authentication, registration, password management, and more. 
    It enables seamless integration with Amazon Cognito for R developers, making it easier to manage user identities and authentication flows.
